Fig. 22F
). Endites brown; labium dark brown. Sternum brownish orange, with darker margins, marbled with dark pigment, and three pairs of dark marginal areas (
Fig. 22G
). Palps brownish yellow, with tibia and tarsus reddish. Legs brownish yellow, with pairs I‒II darker. Metatarsus and tarsus of legs I‒II darker than the other segments. Dark pigment forming diffuse rings in the distal region of tibia, metatarsus and tarsus, of legs I‒II (

Fig. 
22I
‒J

