Fig. 22F‒G
). Total length 9.88; carapace 4.44 long, 2.68 wide. Chelicerae not projected (
Fig. 22F
). Legs: robust and densely coated with setae, mainly on the ventral region of pairs I‒III; legs I‒II with ventro-prolateral and ventro-retrolateral tibial macrosetae of similar size, and metatarsal macrosetae of different sizes (

Fig. 
22I
‒J

). Leg formula: I-II-IV-III. Leg measurements: I, femur 3.04, patella 1.52, tibia 2.36, metatarsus 2.32, tarsus 0.76, total 10.0; II, 2.76, 1.48, 2.32, 2.16, 0.68, 9.4; III, 2.16, 1.24, 1.48, 1.52, 0.6, 7.0; IV, 2.8, 1.56, 2.16, 1.8, 0.64, 8.96. Macrosetae: I, femur P0-0-0-0-0-1-0; tibia vp1-0-1-0-1-0-1, vr1-0-1-0-1-0-1, R0-1-0-0-0-0-0; metatarsus vp1-1-0/ 1-1-1-1-1-1, vr1-1-1-1-1-1-1 (

